Qaddafi Says May Replace Western Oil Firms With Chinese, Indian, Brazilian

-- B y   L o u i s   M e i x l e r
-- 
2011-03-02T13:35:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/qaddafi-says-may-replace-western-oil-firms-with-chinese-indian-brazilian.html
Libyan leader  Muammar Qaddafi  said
he may replace Western oil firms with those from China and  India . He also said the exit of foreign workers leaves jobs for
Libyans. He was speaking on state television today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
